# Phase-level fallout — runs once per tick, after every agent's day pipeline
# has finished (a TickLoop ruleset phase, outside any pipeline: a pipeline
# postHook fires per invocation, i.e. per agent, which would be up to 10x too
# often). Aggregate over the whole store; fixpoint; boolean asserts only.

rule "tension boils over into open feud"
  tension(?X, ?Y) > 8
  ^ tension(?Y, ?X) > 5
  ^ not feuding(?X, ?Y)
  => feuding(?X, ?Y)
